LicenseRef-markusj-upd72020x-load

Upstream: https://github.com/markusj/upd72020x-load (markusj/upd72020x-load)

The upstream Git repository does not ship a LICENSE file. As of 2026-06,
https://github.com/markusj/upd72020x-load/issues/2 remains open asking for
license clarification; the maintainer notes the original loader source came
from a comment on a blog post (Michael Billauer's blog, uPD720202 Linux
firmware discussion) without any copyright notice.

No redistribution grant from upstream is assumed for this Dynamic Devices
packaging. This Yocto recipe documents provenance only; confirm compliance
before redistributing built images containing the loader binaries.

Renesas K2026.mem firmware (proprietary, not redistributable in public BSP) is
shipped separately for imx8mm-jaguar-phasora via meta-subscriber-overrides
(upd72020x-firmware recipe).
